    <briefdescription>
<para>Fitting options, used when resizing images to fit desired dimensions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A fitting mode controls the region of a loaded image to be mapped to the desired image rectangle. All fitting modes preserve the aspect ratio of the image contents. @SINCE_2_5.14 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
